a phosphorous silicate glass layer for limiting mobile ion transport, positioned on top of the third layer; and 
a pair of metal electrodes for providing an ohmic contact wherein a first electrode is positioned below the substrate and a second electrode is positioned above the third layer; 
wherein the avalanche photodiode comprises a first sidewall and a second sidewall forming a sloped mesa shape; and 
